	module.exports = "<section class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste\">\n<h2 class=\"check\" id=\"sjekkliste\">Sjekkliste</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Klar!</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Trykk på Lag en Liste for å lage en ny liste.</p>\n<figure><img src=\"" + __webpack_require__(1149) + "\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Prøv denne koden</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Tøm listen før du starter.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-scratch\">når grønt flagg klikkes\nslett <span class=\"hljs-string\">[all v]</span> i <span class=\"hljs-string\">[noter v]</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Hver gang noe skjer, legg det til listen.</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code class=\"language-scratch\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">n</span>å<span class=\"hljs-tag\">r</span> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">denne</span> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">figuren</span> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">klikkes</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">spill</span> <span class=\"hljs-tag\">tone</span> (<span class=\"hljs-tag\">pitch</span>) <span class=\"hljs-tag\">i</span> (0<span class=\"hljs-class\">.5</span>) <span class=\"hljs-tag\">takter</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">legg</span> (<span class=\"hljs-tag\">pitch</span>) <span class=\"hljs-tag\">til</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr_selector\">[noter v]</span>\n</code></pre>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Hvis du vil ta opp flere ting samtidig, bruk en liste for hver.</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code class=\"language-scratch\">når <span class=\"hljs-string\">[mellomrom v]</span> trykkes\ngå (<span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>) steg\nlegg (x-posisjon) til <span class=\"hljs-string\">[xs v]</span>\nlegg (y-posisjon) til <span class=\"hljs-string\">[ys v]</span>\nslutt\n</code></pre>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>Se “Avspilling” kortet for hvordan man spiller av et opptak.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n";

